Package com.marklogic.flux.api

Interface WriteStructuredDocumentsOptions

All Superinterfaces:
WriteDocumentsOptions<WriteStructuredDocumentsOptions>
public interface WriteStructuredDocumentsOptions extends WriteDocumentsOptions<WriteStructuredDocumentsOptions>
Defines options for writing "structured" documents - i.e. JSON or XML documents created from all the columns in the rows returned by a reader (as opposed to "document" rows where the document is defined by the "content" column).
